I tried to think about this problem, but I never came up with the right concept. 
Even after reading other people's solutions, I couldn't develop a crystal-clear understanding.
The best I could see from the test cases was that we should divide the array into even and odd numbers, 
but I couldn't come up with an algorithm for how to formulate the final answer neatly.
